Package main.scanner

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IScanner
    The IScanner interface specifies operations for reading ITokens from a source file.
    IScannerFactory
    The interface Scanner factory.
    IToken
    The IToken interface specifies operations on the lexical units of a formal language.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractScanner
    The AbstractScanner class provides a minimal implementation of the IScanner interface.
    Position
    The Position class represents a pair of indices that together specify a location in a text file in terms of a line and column number.
